{"tid":2137622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"99%指司法獨立已死 進入一國一制","createTime":"2020-08-03T05:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T05:18:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f809644584c500bb3d8b266490305303a0381123","tid":2137622,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/5C3BW5HYPCG7S3HANEDOAD7MJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2F5C3BW5HYPCG7S3HANEDOAD7MJU%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=eb57db50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2F5C3BW5HYPCG7S3HANEDOAD7MJU%2F&h=5e5e17a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/5C3BW5HYPCG7S3HANEDOAD7MJU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n99%指司法獨立已死 進入一國一制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YDb21WR9Yu-S4ZIOnO26OW6-1fk=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ET66OP7BWD5YQFRD3DPGQFDF4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYDb21WR9Yu-S4ZIOnO26OW6-1fk%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FET66OP7BWD5YQFRD3DPGQFDF4U.jpg&h=8e6f4815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超過99%受訪者指香港司法獨立已蕩然無存。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港區。。。。。。。。。。。問卷結果顯示，超過99%民主派支持者表示認同或完全認同，在國安法之下，香港司法獨立已蕩然無存；亦有超過99%受訪者認同或完全認同，香港已正式進入一國一制時代。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：惡法陰霾 七成人自我審查  市民unfriend刪po 「最恐怖係人與人不信任」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近五成不認同對抗爭絕望<br />\n<br />\n但另一方面，香港人對抗爭並非徹底絕望。合共近五成受訪者不認同或完全不認同「對抗爭感到絕望」，表示認同或完全認同的，則有約三成。調查時民主派參選人尚未被DQ，有48%受訪者仍相信選舉對爭取香港民主自由有其意義，覺得沒意義的則佔約33%。<br />\n<br />\n國。。。。。。。。。。。。當中約38%人選擇特首林鄭月娥，香港警察緊接其後，有約30%。沒有受訪者選擇「反送中運動示威者」、「傳媒」，選擇「泛民主派」的只有一人。有83%受訪者稱對比國安法實施前，現時移民外國意欲有增加，結果較本報今年「五一黃金周」時向黃店食客所作的問卷調查，增約14%。"}]}